{{term|natal indigo}}
{{defn|1=Natal indigo (''Indigofera arrecta'') is an [[indigo dye]]-bearing plant of [[Central America|Central]] and [[South America]].<ref name="Indigo" /><ref name="Goodwin70"/>}}
{{term|natural dye}}
{{defn|1=[[Natural dye]]s are dyes derived from [[animal]]s, [[plant]]s, [[mineral]]s, [[fungus|fungi]] and [[lichens]].<ref>Cannon & Cannon (2002), p. 12</ref>}}
