{{Infobox language |name=Moloko |nativename=''Məlokwo'' |states=[[Cameroon]] |region=[[Far North Province]] |speakers=8,500 |date=1992 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Afro-Asiatic |fam2=[[Chadic languages|Chadic]] |fam3=[[Biu–Mandara languages|Biu–Mandara]] |fam4=Wandala–Mafa |fam5=[[Mafa languages|Mafa]] (A.5) |fam6=South (a) |iso3=mlw |glotto=molo1266 |glottorefname=Moloko }}
'''Moloko''' (Məlokwo) is an [[Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic]] language spoken in northern [[Cameroon]].<ref name=e18/>
== Further reading == Friesen, Dianne. 2017. A grammar of Moloko. Berlin: Language Science Press. 978-3-946234-63-0. DOI 10.5281/zenodo.824016 http://langsci-press.org/catalog/book/118. Open Access.
